@alexanderdecroo @Google @googleeurope @google_belgium @ThGeerts @CCB_Belgium @certbe Thank you PM @alexanderdecroo for a productive discussion today on important topics that are top of mind for all of us. Our teams are working 24/7 to track and disrupt cyber threats and tackle disinformation.

@ThierryBreton Thank you Commissioner @ThierryBreton for your time and the good discussion today about digital regulation. We take seriously our responsibility to tackle misinformation and provide reliable, trustworthy information to people in Ukraine and globally.
